      'Choose 5 daily anchors — moments that reliably occur: first coffee, first bathroom visit, before each meal, red lights, before sleep. These become your triggers.',
      'At each trigger, pause for 15–30 seconds. Ask silently: "Who is aware of this moment?" Rest in the awareness that is aware, not in any thought or sensation.',
      'Log in your metric field how many of your 5 triggers you actually completed. A simple tally mark system works well.',
