    beginner: 'Before touching your phone, write one sentence: "Today I intend to ___." One sentence. That is the entire practice. The discipline is doing it before anything else.',
    measure: 'At day\'s end, score alignment 1–10: how consistently did your choices reflect your morning intention? This score across 30 days reveals the gap between stated intention and lived behavior — and closing that gap is the work.',
